2ba2525a6c0293c0aa3593f8e2f135167224245b.query:
WITH list_view AS (
        SELECT
            id,
            ao,
            to_jsonb(string_to_array(q, ',')) as q,
            to_jsonb(string_to_array(pax, ',')) as pax,
            date,
            bb_type
        FROM back_blasts
    )
    
    SELECT id, ao, q, pax, date, bb_type
    FROM list_view 
    WHERE bb_type = 'backblast'
    ORDER BY date DESC;

f22a6fed2db3c20b00cecb56e9a43fdcf20aefa7.query:
WITH list_view AS (
        SELECT
            id,
            ao,
            to_jsonb(string_to_array(q, ',')) as q,
            to_jsonb(string_to_array(pax, ',')) as pax,
            date,
            bb_type
        FROM back_blasts
    )
    
    SELECT id, ao, q, pax, date, bb_type
    FROM list_view 
    WHERE pax ?| array[$1] AND bb_type = 'backblast'
    ORDER BY date DESC;
